platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This games cheeky hilarity comes from the endlessly unexpected ways we perish during our trek to the zombie-free haven north of the 49th. Smashing our car in an ill-advised stunt jump, being abandoned by our rifle-toting dog, losing a pose-off to a bunch of burly banditsyou get the picture. This undead action-adventure just wont stop gnawing on our funnybones.
